cast
Homonym Number:
Word Class:adjective
Sense Number: 1
Definition:[of sheep] turned on to their backs and unable to rise [resulting in possible attack by seagulls and other birds, fly-strike and starvation.]
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
